{"data":{"page":{"id":"9bbd65d5-3cdc-518a-af6e-19db30d19b89","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/local7/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived website without DB</a>\n</p>\n<p>Local7 contacted us (Webmarket) to build an online shop to sell their products. They wanted a very personal style combined with great UX and an easy payment method.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 34.9%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/f74889145875ba4821fde11b64d3079b/6b333/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f74889145875ba4821fde11b64d3079b/f3ce7/1.jpg 200w,\n/static/f74889145875ba4821fde11b64d3079b/72342/1.jpg 400w,\n/static/f74889145875ba4821fde11b64d3079b/6b333/1.jpg 800w,\n/static/f74889145875ba4821fde11b64d3079b/40247/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>At this point, I didn’t have a system or CMS with this sort of functionality. The open source options available at that time were also very insufficient for the requirements, so I decided to build my own bespoke solution. I called it TIENDAFlash, because it was based in Flash, PHP and MySQL.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 63.3%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6450db87c4e76d73648a63633b1e2d8c/6b333/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6450db87c4e76d73648a63633b1e2d8c/f3ce7/2.jpg 200w,\n/static/6450db87c4e76d73648a63633b1e2d8c/72342/2.jpg 400w,\n/static/6450db87c4e76d73648a63633b1e2d8c/6b333/2.jpg 800w,\n/static/6450db87c4e76d73648a63633b1e2d8c/40247/2.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>TIENDAFlash allows the maximum flexibility in the front-end and a very compatible and extended tech stack for the backend. It also features a custom CMS to add/edit/remove products, categories, photos and customers. I also implemented a credit/debit card payment gateway using the API from ServiRed (a very popular banking network in Spain).</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 800px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 69.8874296435272%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"5\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9a5404d9a4a5ebf30b291dc75c093bbe/6b333/5.jpg\"